headline: Keysight Joins Forces with Singapore’s Quantum Leaders to Advance Capabilities in the Design and Control of Qubits
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., December 18, 2025--Keysight has signed a five-year Master Research Collaboration Agreement (MRCA) with Singapore’s leading quantum research institutions.
